Before release:
- Test that errors can cross DLL boundaries
- Copyright notices on files
- COPYING file
- License information in the manual
- Split it all into a separate git repo

Features:
- Support radix sorting for signed and floating-point values
- Support scans that write back to a different array from input (with different type)
- Sort and scan from an offset into an array
- Custom computation of sort keys or scan values
- Custom reduction operators for scan
- Custom types for sort values (not just builtin types)
- True multi-scan (not limited to vector scan)
- Add standalone benchmarking app
- Cache compiled kernels in some way, or allow cloning
- Interleaved key-value pairs
